*DESCRIPTION_START
Gilt-edged paintings of voluptuous women reclining in sylvan settings adorn
the red-velvet wallpapered walls. Fringed lampshades and ornate furniture
give this parlor a Victorian aire. A door leads to a private room.
*DESCRIPTION_END

;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
;Bathroom
NUMBER 1297
 NAME Hotel Escapades, Massage Parlor Bathroom
 REGION 0
 INDOOR_FLOOR
 FIXED_LIGHT
 CHANNEL 1

*DESCRIPTION_START
Flickering candlelight illuminates this plush bathroom with a warm glow,
revealing a marble sink, large Roman bathtub, gold and velvet wallpaper and
heavy towels.
*DESCRIPTION_END

 EXIT O 1299
 ; Door
 ITEM 0 352 VAL2=1299 UNLOCKED

 IFVERB SNIFF -1
  ECHO PLAYER Your nose is treated with the aroma of a fragrant potpourri.
  ECHO OTHERS %N sniffs the fragrant scent of the potpourri.
 ENDIF
